If you hurt Claire...

490
00:40:21.219 --> 00:40:22.653
Hurt Claire?

491
00:40:24.923 --> 00:40:27.358
Have you been
listening at all. Ryan?

492
00:40:27.892 --> 00:40:30.020
I love Claire.

493
00:40:30.194 --> 00:40:34.689
She's on her way to me now. By
all accounts she came quite willingly.

494
00:40:44.575 --> 00:40:46.942
I'm done. Joe. I quit.

495
00:40:47.111 --> 00:40:51.947
Oh. come. come. That's no way to
talk to the man who saved your life.

496
00:40:52.884 --> 00:40:55.581
<i>I've allowed you
a second chance.</i>

497
00:40:56.454 --> 00:40:59.424
Don't you understand
anything yet...

498
00:41:00.058 --> 00:41:01.287
Ryan?

499
00:41:02.193 --> 00:41:04.560
No. this is your story. your...

500
00:41:04.963 --> 00:41:06.454
Your rebirth.

501
00:41:07.298 --> 00:41:08.561
Don't you feel it?

502
00:41:09.200 --> 00:41:11.226
<i>With every death...</i>

503
00:41:11.402 --> 00:41:15.567
<i>you come just a little
bit more back to life.</i>

504
00:41:15.807 --> 00:41:20.245
So. no. No. you can't quit now.

505
00:41:20.611 --> 00:41:25.208
No. you're... You're not quite
yet the man you need to be.

506
00:41:30.088 --> 00:41:32.080
You go to hell.

507
00:41:47.638 --> 00:41:51.234
Don't push her away. You
gotta stop with this death curse.

508
00:41:55.813 --> 00:41:57.839
It's crazy to think that way.

509
00:41:58.249 --> 00:42:00.343
You can let people
get close to you.

510
00:42:00.852 --> 00:42:02.445
I mean. look at us.

511
00:42:02.754 --> 00:42:05.451
I'm practically your wife.
you haven't gotten me killed.

512
00:42:05.623 --> 00:42:07.067
- Heh.
- We've been together over 20 years...

513
00:42:07.091 --> 00:42:08.957
I'm still standing.

514
00:42:10.495 --> 00:42:12.020
Nobody wants to die alone.

515
00:42:14.132 --> 00:42:18.194
- We all die alone.
- All the more reason not to live that way.

516
00:42:18.870 --> 00:42:21.999
- Well. hey. I've got you.
- Heh. yes. you do.

517
00:42:23.441 --> 00:42:25.467
All right. love
birds. food's ready.

518
00:42:51.035 --> 00:42:52.230
- Uh. Joe?
- Hmm.

519
00:42:59.343 --> 00:43:00.402
Molly.

520
00:43:01.879 --> 00:43:02.903
Joe.

521
00:43:03.347 --> 00:43:04.645
It's so good to see you.
